&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/underflowerror/"&gt;std::underflow_error&lt;/a&gt; — arithmetic underflow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/cpp/rangeerror/"&gt;std::range_error&lt;/a&gt; — range errors in computations.&lt;/li&gt;
